{"tid":121252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七警早餐都有雞翼食呀","createTime":"2017-02-15T05:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T06:10:14.000Z","uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59196edce048524cfad0f1571de1ef364df8304f","tid":121252,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】7名警察在佔領運動時襲擊示威者罪成，昨被即時還押荔枝角收押所。熟悉懲教院所運作人士指出，七警這類特殊個案，還押初期一般會獲安排入住院所的醫院病房內，7人還押院內時毋須分隔處理。昨日情人節，院所沒有特別安排，晚餐菜式除了魚、瓜、白飯，以及茶及橙，周二會加雞蛋；<span style=\"color: red;\">今天（周三）則有雞翼配飯作早餐及紅豆粥作午餐。</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早餐都有雞翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚餐一定好豐富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da1347ee7d5ba8c1370bc4065789c9dd457d070","tid":121252,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T06:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fdfeda350d7913cd69c95d5a2db7b663d4d91f","tid":121252,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01e6345a12c9696a4cbb0cd87c4f8c2187e49ad","tid":121252,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"好過好多人"},{"pid":"73ce115cbe0db33b3ab55b71fb4ac3ff1f96cc9b","tid":121252,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"報紙佬可以將早餐同午餐調轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03da1d3bd34c2c6391a433a1e927d525c9f17157","tid":121252,"uid":421